philosophers application (erlang version)

to compile and run this application do the following:

- install the erlang (on ubuntu linux e.g.  sudo apt-get install erlang)
- open a termnial window and navigate to this directory
- open erlang shell by simply typing erl into the command line, e.g.:

	user@ubuntu:~/Documents/code$ erl

- when the shell starts, type the following to compile the erlang source code:

c(philosophers).

- to run the application, type:

philosophers:dinner().


